These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-1::.
Food: mango, pepper, pomegranate, raspberry
Game: billiard, bridge, go, scrabble
1. Game:bridge is on the left of Game:billiard##1
2. Food:mango == Game:scrabble##1
3. Game:go is on the right of Game:billiard##1
4. Food:pepper is on the left of Game:scrabble##1
5. Food:raspberry is on the left of Game:billiard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Food          | raspberry | pomegranate | pepper | mango   |
| Game   | bridge  | billiard     | go   | scrabble |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-2::.
Hobby: camping, cooking, video-games, woodworking
Game: billiard, whist, snooker, bridge
1. Hobby:woodworking == Game:whist##1
2. Hobby:camping is on the far right##1
3. Hobby:cooking is on the right of Hobby:woodworking##1
4. Hobby:woodworking is on the right of Game:snooker##1
5. Game:whist is on the left of Game:billiard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby   | video-games | woodworking | cooking | camping    |
| Game   | snooker    | whist      | billiard | bridge |

